data.name: DropDownAccessibleShortcut
data.comment: Keyboard shortcut for opening the drop-down in place edit control. Displayed to the user by accessibility tools.

data.name: DropDownButtonAccessibleName
data.comment: Accessible name used for the down-arrow button in the in-place edit control. Displayed to the user by accessibility tools.

data.name: BrowseButtonAccessibleName
data.comment: Accessible name used for the "..." button in the in-place edit control. Displayed to the user by accessibility tools.

data.name: DuplicateColumnException
data.comment: Exception message thrown if user tries to add a column to the tree that already exists.

data.name: InvalidColumnOrderArrayException
data.value: The order array lengths must match each other and the VisibleColumnCount property.
data.comment: Exception message. VisibleColumnCount should not be localized, it is an API property name.

data.name: HeaderArrayException
data.value: Length of headers array must match the current column count.
data.comment: Exception message.

data.name: BlankSubItemException
data.value: A blank item cannot have sub items.
data.comment: Exception message.

data.name: ColumnOutOfRangeException
data.value: Row parameter must be >= 0 if column > 0.
data.comment: Exception message. column is a parameter name and should not be localized.

data.name: ComplexColumnRootException
data.value: Parameter complexColumnRoot should only be true for items in the top list of a complex subitem.
data.comment: Exception message. complexColumnRoot is a parameter names and should not be localized.

data.name: ParentRowException
data.value: Parameter parentRow does not indicate a row with children.
data.comment: Exception message. parentRow is a parameter name and should not be localized.

data.name: ComplexColumnCellStyleException
data.value: The cell style for the indicated column must be Complex or Mixed.
data.comment: Exception message.

data.name: PercentageBasedHeadersInvalidException
data.value: Percentage based columns must form an ascending sequence of positive numbers <=1.
data.comment: Exception message.

data.name: PercentageBasedHeadersLastInvalidException
data.value: The last percentage in a set of percentage-based columns must be 1.
data.comment: Exception message.

data.name: SelectionModeNoneException
data.comment: Exception message.

data.name: RowAccDesc
data.comment: Accessibility description. 0:d is a format specifier, replaced with row index at runtime.

data.name: ColumnAccDesc
data.comment: Accessibility description. 0:d is a format specifier, replaced with column index at runtime.

data.name: ColumnNumberAccDesc
data.comment: Accessibility description. 0:d is a format specifier, replaced with number of total columns at runtime.

data.name: ChildRowNumberAccDesc
data.comment: Accessibility description. 0:d is a format specifier, replaced with number of child rows at runtime.

data.name: RowOfTotalAccDesc
data.comment: Accessibility description. 0:d and 1:d are format specifiers, replaced with row index and total row count at runtime, respectively.

data.name: RowColumnAccDesc
data.comment: Accessibility description. 0:d and 1:d are format specifiers, replaced with row index and column index at runtime, respectively.

data.comment: Accessibility action description.
